Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本那么温柔 那么强大的人却…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是那样 其实他很软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没能保护好他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为自己能让他从这个世界逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他杀了许多自己人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他很弱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 只能沉默不语 或随之疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 为什么都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做这种事情我也不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想让丸太你来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快闪开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 这种程度白是不会痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么弱 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋丸太 快闪开吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样 看着朋友被红衣男杀掉 渣到根了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 「没有时间去考虑复仇」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你对我说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是「只要还有希望」 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…我的光芒 已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有黑暗 和憎恨!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪的痛苦 其实我无法体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是死了的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀掉的家伙再也回不来了 这种悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞和懊悔 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 凪的周围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全是光芒在闪耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你一直都低着头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连这种事都搞不清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪的身边不是有很多光芒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 光芒…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的希望已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的光 至今还在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 虽然做了很多过分的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我很弱 即使这是个疯狂的地方 也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 会保护我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫血? ?不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了 身体…麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:07:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 最后一次吃「Candy」是什么时候来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 「猫头鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我挺起腰杆啊 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那铃声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表我也有着重要的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 唐子 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哭要赎罪 等逃出这里后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别泡我的修罗 你这混蛋女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大呼小叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难得让她得到了救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个想要见见自己孩子的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个一心想要帮助别人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜 生 艹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不起作用?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧 想我救你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我避开了心脏和肺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该刺进骨头里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由你来把她送上西天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是她最好的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是憎恨一切 用杀戮来救赎的修罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是个软弱的人类罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 怎会是救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的救赎 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 为了自由而并肩作战的同伴就在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吧 「猫头鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯掉的你很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀戮的身影也很迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾爱着你呦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要变回那个无法普度众生的混帐伪君子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来将你救赎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊 弦角…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布施的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又到镇上和人打架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为你是个温驯稳重的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶因只会招致恶果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不恨他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个扭曲的现世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懦弱地不幸地 陷于无上的愚蠢之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普度众生的方法是否存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻悟真的就能逃脱生老病死么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么佛祖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道什么是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却认定死亡是痛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 救救 我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,益信 午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白 如何普度众生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静寂就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安宁即是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执枉也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善美都是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻悟也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡才是救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吉 晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是挣扎着想逃出去的「Deadman」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能望着外界死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好的坟墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒素蔓延 很痛苦吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地下就是你们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恐惧中 僵化狂暴地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身沾满了着罪和五脏六腑而死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才能得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我这个超级和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来赐予你们拯救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.51,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(729,653)}Grateful Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚空一闪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.70,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,653)}Invisible Black
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度就裂开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 他们必须被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 必须要哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我 什么都做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挂掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜小猫还是做掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到被救赎之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直拯救下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧 压抑 背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望 侮辱 后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤 痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯狂 痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会从fucking的世界中拯救你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 轮到我当Ace Man了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的大家都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要有朋友在 就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有闲工夫找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的救赎么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十岚 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎 已经用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然充满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖的雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会出现美丽的彩虹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你不出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过很想出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能丢下朋友不管的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 之前打了你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我 还做了过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 已经不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还一起看到了闪闪轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后有机会一起坐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 还有哪里痛么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是糖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这件事以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角他们居然这么不顶用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色很不好啊 创办人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被死囚逃狱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 莳名小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的管辖区内没有少哪一个囚犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是还不习惯当所长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没经过交接 他突然就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我的管辖区内没有少人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580号五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和9061号鹰见羊都回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这11天里 他们去了哪里 干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去审问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看情况也许会上点家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没你的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会听到趣事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揉肩膀么 莳名长官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人选定好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从创始人名簿上的一般犯人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出了一名最合适人选
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有那么强的「罪之枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么味道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:23:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做尽坏事的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也在不停地啄 森林已是千疮百孔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发怒了的森林之神 将它的喙变成了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦恼的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巢穴染上了毒 食物也染上了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友碰到它 全都相继地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩有毒的泪水闪烁着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:23:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:24:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是丸太的妈妈写的歌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.97,0:24:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很怀念 但还是别唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…红衣男也唱了这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.75,0:24:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那个家伙 为什么会知道这首歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

