Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:37.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}流星 black & night
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:40.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪止不住 一直流
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.90,0:24:49.29,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恨 恨这不公的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.35,0:24:57.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这座迷宫 想逃 却没有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.86,0:25:01.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追求自由的我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:11.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}倒立着 俯看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.45,0:25:18.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我已经不是昨天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.25,0:25:25.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 夜空洒遍了星辉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.01,0:25:34.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界竟如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.56,0:25:41.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 月光载满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.22,0:25:49.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界是这般精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:51.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不是吗?


